text: Soup was flavourful but rather diluted. At $6.80, there were only two halves of a small prawn as well as ribs with barely any meat. Staff was friendly.
Had my brunch at Laing Zai Prawn Noodle. Prawns are fresh and Pork ribs & Tails are tendered. Highly recommended üëç
This is really a good prawn noodle. The food is very fresh. The service is also very good. A very happy lunch
